\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
However, some are at the basis of what differentiates one individual from
 the other.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
Polymorphisms can involve base substitutions, insertions, deletions, or
 repeats.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
Generally, they are distinguished by sequence and length polymorphisms.
 
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
The functional effect of any given DNA polymorphism on a phenotype can range
 from fully penetrant (1 mutation, 1 effect) to none.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
For most traits of agricultural interest, which are mostly complex or multifacto
rial traits, the penetrance is intermediate to low.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


